steps.name: I click on Create your Account with selector "a[href='#/setup/two/']"
I expect to enter to Create your Account screen "<GHOST-VERSION-1-SETUP2>"
I enter Site title "Pruebas Automatizadas MISO" into selector "input[name='blog-title']"
I enter Full Name "Robot de prueba" into selector "input[name='name']"
I push login button with selector "button[type='submit']"
I click on Skip option with selector "button[class='gh-flow-skip']"
